d3treeR

Example from https://github.com/timelyportfolio/d3treeR

Data

library(treemap)
library(d3treeR)
data(GNI2014)

knitr::kable(head(GNI2014, row.names = FALSE))

Treemap

tm <- treemap(GNI2014, 
              index=c("continent", "iso3"), 
              vSize="population", 
              vColor="GNI", 
              type="value")

d3 treemap

d3tree(tm, rootname = "World")
